Surgret Urania DOSS, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
DEPARTMENT OF REVENUE, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-3388 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. October 17, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

This appeal is dismissed because of the appellant's failure to satisfy this court's August 23, 2018 fee order. Appellee's motion to dismiss is denied as moot.

KHOUZAM, ROTHSTEIN-YOUAKIM, and ATKINSON, JJ., Concur.
